{"tid":728972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打啦打啦] 消息指中國將在周五起向340億美元美國商品徵稅","createTime":"2018-07-04T07:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T01:31:33.000Z","uid":42921,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9ffef559d1d69f2de32d2cc0d389638202e2a9","tid":728972,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"美國政府提出向總值500億美元的中國商品，徵收25%關稅，其中首批340億美元中國商品，將本月六日，即星期五起開始徵收，中國亦隨即宣布，同一日起向相同價值的美國商品，徵收同額的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》引述中方消息人士報道，中國加稅措施，將在星期五零時起生效。<br />\n<br />\n由於兩國時差關係，中國將較美國早12小時實施加稅措施。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，中方的措施是平等的，意味如果美國在星期五開始，他們也將同日開始，所有徵稅施當日零時起生效。"},{"pid":"7e7cb83908ab6250937d404c7b055ae08b784a3b","tid":728972,"uid":42921,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"早過美國開始，又贏"},{"pid":"6ba03ba8ae1f3175e7474807c1738d7437ff8d54","tid":728972,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0db90452a9ae6044a614682819e394ed5df329","tid":728972,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"早過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887caa2a3405d6edabd775e50747170c3d68ec95","tid":728972,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g